<item>
            <title>[LU-13537] DoM: Commit d7073b8 causes significant stat performance degradation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13537</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Introduced in 2.11.56, patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com33233/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com33233/&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11427&quot; title=&quot;Data on MDT performance tune&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11427&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11427&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; lod: create layout in mdo_create()&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;,&#160;while increasing read performance, has introduced a significant degradation with mdtest stat performance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mdtest stat results before the commit:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;MDT0:&#160; 349803.384
MDT1:&#160; 342253.747
MDT2:&#160; 347820.775
MDT3:&#160; 323354.925&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mdtest stat results after the commit:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;MDT0:&#160; 109842.167
MDT1:&#160; 114794.457
MDT2:&#160; 104197.950
MDT3:&#160; 108848.941&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
