                            <comment id="351309" author="koutoupis" created="Mon, 31 Oct 2022 20:09:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Colin,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In a way, yes. We reverted it on our end; as it continues to show a regression with our test systems and even larger cluster deployments. I am not sure what you want to do here. If you believe that the issue should be closed, I won&apos;t argue. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
