&lt;p&gt;Was this ever resolved on your side?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="269980" author="spitzcor" created="Tue, 12 May 2020 20:48:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=Jinshan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;Jinshan&quot;&gt;Jinshan&lt;/a&gt;, did you have a take on this?  Did you expect the stat regression given the boost in reads that you provided with that change?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
